high_descs: Turn around and walk left past the counter. Then straight to the counter near the toaster.
Pick up the tomato to the left of the toaster.
Turn around and take a step to the fridge and face it.
Place the tomato in the fridge to the right of the lettuce. Close the door, wiat a moment, and take it out again.
Take a step right to the microwave.
Place the tomato in the microwave near the center.
anns.task_desc: Place a tomato in a microwave.

high_descs: Go to the right, turn right near the door, walk straight to the counter top with a toaster.
Pick up the tomato on top of the counter top near the toaster.
Turn around and turn right to go to the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the tomato in it, close the fridge, let it cool for a while, pick it up again and close the fridge.
Go to the right to go to the microwave which is beside the fridge.
Open the microwave, Put the tomato in the microwave and close it.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold tomato in the microwave next to the fridge.

high_descs: Turn to the right and walk to the door, then take a right and walk across the room to face the counter.
Pick up the tomato on the counter.
Turn to the left to face the fridge.
Cool the tomato in the fridge and then remove it.
Turn to the left to face the microwave.
Place the tomato in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: To cool a tomato and place it in the microwave.
